      "body" : "I think... the best way in fact should be to have a mixed prune mode.\r\nUsing prune, instead of removing files, archiving it to a second storage. It takes not a lot of code modification I think.\r\nIn that case, it become possible to put everything in SSD drive with -arcprune=<n>, to run with the best speed and to keep full block chain.",
