      "author_association" : "NONE",
      "body" : "I understand.\r\nIn my case corruption was on an index file, so I had to do it or load from empty folder.\r\nIn any case, first load (and future corrections) is too long. Speed is slowing down and is now near 5mn per block file.\r\nIt can be discouraging for many people.\r\nI think that my sugestion can be a good test to do to improve speed.\r\nI started like this so I will wait till the end (in few days, hope no error), but if you don't implemant this, I will do it myself (but it would be better done by a pro).",
